{"tid":14930,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"中資英國MMORPG Runescape [1] LIHKG新post","createTime":"2016-11-30T17:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T15:39:35.000Z","uid":45174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"073e607fefdb1847e7246c97294e737643441008","tid":14930,"uid":45174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:10:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://holland.pk/yrx50jlp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyrx50jlp&h=bdaa804a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">請注意：本post只討論RS3, OSRS玩家請自行另外開post</div></span></strong></span><br />\n遊戲官網：<a href=\"http://www.runescape.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.runescape.com&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9oksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=fa76738f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.runescape.com</a><br />\nGolden Son公會網 (<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">必看<span style=\"color: red;\">新手解難</span></span>): <a href=\"https://rs-hkg.rf.gd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs-hkg.rf.gd&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9oksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=7b46d2f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://rs-hkg.rf.gd</a><br />\n請注意：網站加載需時，請耐心等候<br />\n</div><br />\n《RuneScape》是由英國Jagex採用<del>Java</del> C語言 開發的基於網頁的大型多人線上角色扮演遊戲(可以用客戶端玩)，在世界上很受歡迎，尤其是英國及美國。2016年3月，Jagex 被某強國採礦公司收購，但暫時不影響業務運作。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://holland.pk/3umxcnpq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3umxcnpq&h=ab5ea680&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"http://holland.pk/tvy72nmu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftvy72nmu&h=2c3bf4b4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n====================================<br />\n遊戲平台: PC (Windows/Mac/Linux)<br />\n主要遊戲語言：<span style=\"color: red;\">英文</span><br />\n====================================<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遊戲官網</span>(公式網站): <span style=\"color: purple;\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <a href=\"http://www.runescape.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.runescape.com&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9oksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=fa76738f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.runescape.com</a> <span style=\"color: purple;\">&lt;&lt;&lt;</span><br />\n由於係英文game既關係，中文網站資源少之又少，絕大部分網站都係英文，敬請留意！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />g <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />g <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://holland.pk/ov9rgs15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fov9rgs15&h=b651d517&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n遊戲客戶端(game client)下載：(本地暫存檔local cache需要<span style=\"color: red;\">10GB</span> 硬碟空間, 會在執行客戶端後自動背景下載，不影響遊戲運行，不需另外等候)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遊戲下載</span></span>: <a href=\"https://www.runescape.com/download?jptg=ia&amp;jptv=navbar\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.runescape.com%2Fdownload%3Fjptg%3Dia%26jptv%3Dnavbar&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9oksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=7edc5eb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.runescape.com/download?jptg=ia&amp;jptv=navbar</a><br />\n================================================<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"http://holland.pk/d4wj027a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fd4wj027a&h=5f681460&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"http://holland.pk/y26w7nzl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fy26w7nzl&h=f5a16c72&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">英語苦手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />g 玩家注意：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>呢隻game只有英文</strong></span>（有德文法文係無中文）<br />\n如有語言困難請用Dr.Eye 字典<br />\n<a href=\"http://yun.dreye.com/dict_new/dict.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyun.dreye.com%2Fdict_new%2Fdict.php&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9oksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=62bdf6b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://yun.dreye.com/dict_new/dict.php</a><br />\nYahoo字典<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.dictionary.yahoo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.dictionary.yahoo.com&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9oksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=0f687345\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.dictionary.yahoo.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">太耐無玩過既玩家注意：</span><br />\n依家已經無人會用網頁玩，請download客戶端 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />g <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />g <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />g <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新玩家注意：</span><br />\n現在Runescape已經進行客戶端大更新（又稱NXT），棄用舊式(legacy) Java client，新client NXT不需要Java運行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新玩家建議用NXT進行遊戲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有問題問之前請先睇本公會網既<span style=\"color: red;\">新手解難</span>:</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />g <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />g <br />\n<a href=\"https://rs-hkg.rf.gd/newhand.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs-hkg.rf.gd%2Fnewhand.html&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9oksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=5d7d75db\" target=\"_blank\">https://rs-hkg.rf.gd/newhand.html</a>"},{"pid":"2b0c5d8670fc64919f91cfe5699527f7bcac6dab","tid":14930,"uid":3764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:36:51.000Z","msg":"Os個ac比人爆左就無玩"},{"pid":"86f9107b5971e07a3954a18f7f92879b95c495a9","tid":14930,"uid":45174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T19:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Os個ac比人爆左就無玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n快D加入rs3 啦 好好玩